org.fest.swing.fixture
Interface FrameLikeFixture

All Superinterfaces:
WindowLikeContainerFixture
All Known Implementing Classes:
FrameFixture, JInternalFrameFixture
public interface FrameLikeFixture
extends WindowLikeContainerFixture

Understands functional testing of frame-like components (not necessarily subclasses of Frame):

  • user input simulation
  • state verification
  • property value query

Author:
Yvonne Wang, Alex Ruiz
